testtool.model.database

Class TestToolDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • testtool.model.database.TestToolDB

  • public class TestToolDB
extends java.lang.Object
    The TestToolDb is the top-level data class for the Test Tool. It encapsulates the following structures: a reference to each database object (QuestionDB, CourseDB, etc), and an ActiveUserData object, containing all data relevant to the active user.
